{"name":"Limited Degree","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Your Affliction is limited to no more than two degrees of effect. With two applications of this modifier, it is limited to no more than one degree of effect.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>Your Affliction is limited to no more than two degrees of effect. With two applications of this modifier, it is limited to no more than one degree of effect.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"d98c4vhch9r"}
{"name":"Activation","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>A power with this flaw requires an action to prepare or activate before any of its effects are usable. Move action is –1 point, standard action is –2 points.</p><p>Flat -1 or -2 points.</p>","notes":"<p>A power with this flaw requires an action to prepare or activate before any of its effects are usable. Move action is –1 point, standard action is –2 points.</p><p>Flat -1 or -2 points.</p>","cout":{"rang":0,"parrang":0,"total":-1}},"_id":"leu6jtza1e"}
{"name":"Instant Recovery","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>The target of an Affliction effect with this modifier recovers automatically, no check required, at the end of the round in which the duration ends.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>The target of an Affliction effect with this modifier recovers automatically, no check required, at the end of the round in which the duration ends.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"rlc4zo6lren"}
{"name":"Check Required","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>An effect with this flaw requires a check of some sort—usually a skill check—with a base difficulty of 10, +1 for each additional rank in Check Required.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>An effect with this flaw requires a check of some sort—usually a skill check—with a base difficulty of 10, +1 for each additional rank in Check Required.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"zwm1digxxro"}
{"name":"Concentration","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Using a Concentration effect requires more concentration than normal. If you are unable to maintain your concentration, the effect ends.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>Using a Concentration effect requires more concentration than normal. If you are unable to maintain your concentration, the effect ends.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"rm3g3i8f10p"}
{"name":"Diminished Range","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Each rank of this flaw reduces the effect’s range increments by one step.</p><p>Flat -1 point per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>Each rank of this flaw reduces the effect’s range increments by one step.</p><p>Flat -1 point per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"m6cvifxx5as"}
{"name":"Distracting","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Using a Distracting effect requires so much concentration or effort that you are vulnerable until the start of your next turn.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>Using a Distracting effect requires so much concentration or effort that you are vulnerable until the start of your next turn.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"x09a1t2ysha"}
{"name":"Grab-Based","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>An attack with this flaw requires you to successfully grab and hold a target before the effect can be used.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>An attack with this flaw requires you to successfully grab and hold a target before the effect can be used.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"aojucup7c1q"}
{"name":"Increased Action","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Each rank of this flaw increases the action required to use an effect by one step (Free to Move, Move to Standard, etc.).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>Each rank of this flaw increases the action required to use an effect by one step (Free to Move, Move to Standard, etc.).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"p8u434gf089"}
{"name":"Limited","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>An effect with this flaw only works under certain circumstances, or has a significant restriction on its use.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>An effect with this flaw only works under certain circumstances, or has a significant restriction on its use.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"q41ej6yo3xj"}
{"name":"Noticeable","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>A continuous or permanent effect with this flaw is very noticeable (glows, makes a loud noise, etc.).</p><p>Flat -1 point.</p>","notes":"<p>A continuous or permanent effect with this flaw is very noticeable (glows, makes a loud noise, etc.).</p><p>Flat -1 point.</p>","cout":{"rang":0,"parrang":0,"total":-1}},"_id":"0pojy9wq47ep"}
{"name":"Quirk","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>A Quirk is a minor flaw, often something specific to a character or power, that doesn’t quite rise to the level of a full -1 cost per rank flaw.</p><p>Flat -1 point.</p>","notes":"<p>A Quirk is a minor flaw, often something specific to a character or power, that doesn’t quite rise to the level of a full -1 cost per rank flaw.</p><p>Flat -1 point.</p>","cout":{"rang":0,"parrang":0,"total":-1}},"_id":"8bwphnyu9s6"}
{"name":"Reduced Range","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Each rank of this flaw reduces the range of an effect (Ranged to Close, etc.).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>Each rank of this flaw reduces the range of an effect (Ranged to Close, etc.).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"x2uq2jq2ij"}
{"name":"Resistible","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>An effect with this flaw allows an additional resistance check, or is resisted by a different defense than usual.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>An effect with this flaw allows an additional resistance check, or is resisted by a different defense than usual.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"hojd6izqqeq"}
{"name":"Sense-Dependent","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>The target must be able to perceive the effect with a particular sense for it to work.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>The target must be able to perceive the effect with a particular sense for it to work.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"x9akevlzf4k"}
{"name":"Side Effect","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>If you fail to use the effect properly, or even if you succeed, you suffer a negative side effect.</p><p>–1 or –2 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>If you fail to use the effect properly, or even if you succeed, you suffer a negative side effect.</p><p>–1 or –2 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"ycjdrgaqwl"}
{"name":"Tiring","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Using the effect is physically or mentally taxing, causing you to become fatigued.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>Using the effect is physically or mentally taxing, causing you to become fatigued.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"fk01v1rxhlg"}
{"name":"Uncontrolled","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have no control over when the effect activates or what it does; the GM decides.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>You have no control over when the effect activates or what it does; the GM decides.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"bi5oy16d6p"}
{"name":"Unreliable","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>An Unreliable effect only works some of the time (5 uses, or requires a check each time).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>An Unreliable effect only works some of the time (5 uses, or requires a check each time).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"1sgigmb1lzj"}
{"name":"Feedback","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You suffer damage when a manifestation of your effect is damaged.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>You suffer damage when a manifestation of your effect is damaged.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"hlymwlqxutt"}
{"name":"Inaccurate","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>An effect with this flaw is hard to control or wildly inaccurate. Each rank gives you a –2 penalty to attack checks.</p><p>Flat -1 point per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>An effect with this flaw is hard to control or wildly inaccurate. Each rank gives you a –2 penalty to attack checks.</p><p>Flat -1 point per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"w6replkgjof"}
{"name":"Permanent","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>A continuous effect with this flaw becomes permanent in duration. It cannot be turned off and cannot be improved using extra effort.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","notes":"<p>A continuous effect with this flaw becomes permanent in duration. It cannot be turned off and cannot be improved using extra effort.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"rang":1,"parrang":-1,"total":-1}},"_id":"oxif5efxknj"}
{"name":"Removable","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Removable applies to the power as a whole. The flaw is worth –1 point per 5 total power points.</p><p>Flat -1 point per 5 points.</p>","notes":"<p>Removable applies to the power as a whole. The flaw is worth –1 point per 5 total power points.</p><p>Flat -1 point per 5 points.</p>","cout":{"rang":0,"parrang":0,"total":-1}},"_id":"6dluimk05i"}
{"name":"Easily Removable","type":"pouvoir","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"description":"<p>An easily removable power can be taken away with a disarm or grab action. The flaw is worth –2 points per 5 total power points.</p><p>Flat -2 points per 5 points.</p>","notes":"<p>An easily removable power can be taken away with a disarm or grab action. The flaw is worth –2 points per 5 total power points.</p><p>Flat -2 points per 5 points.</p>","cout":{"rang":0,"parrang":0,"total":-2}},"_id":"0slrxkq7le8p"}